      "kind": "heading",
      "text": "Cascade Orienteering Club Membership Information",
      "text_length": 48
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1980-01_02-list_item-92519bbf3f-1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "text": "Individual: $4.00",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1980-01_02-list_item-475a86eeee-1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "text": "Family: $7.00",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1980-01_02-paragraph-e38b540c40-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "The Cascade Orienteering Club is now in its fourth year and continues to grow. If you would like to join in the fun and learn this sport, we would be happy to have you as a member. We would also be happy to have help on some of our committees, so if you would like to help, then let us know your interests. Please check the box below:",
      "text_length": 334
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1980-01_02-list_item-8c4b19a8a3-1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "text": "[ ] Publicity",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1980-01_02-list_item-bc37b5117e-1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "text": "[ ] Training",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1980-01_02-list_item-04ba09b249-1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "text": "[ ] Events - making maps",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1980-01_02-list_item-8365e8ff04-1",
      "kind": "list_item",
      "text": "[ ] Events - site selection",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1980-01_02-heading-7f1f888f42-1",
      "kind": "heading",
      "text": "COMING EVENTS",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1980-01_02-heading-89ddb11840-1",
      "kind": "heading",
      "text": "Meet",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1980-01_02-paragraph-960dbaf2d2-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "Saturday, January 19, 10 AM",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1980-01_02-paragraph-cc15de6356-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "First Orienteering meet of 1980. Place: Lower Woodland Park. Meet at the picnic area at 10 AM. Directors: Goren Larssen and Dave Enger. Beginners and Intermediate courses using International symbols and for the first time a four-colored map. Wowee.",
      "text_length": 248
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1980-01_02-heading-89ddb11840-2",
      "kind": "heading",
      "text": "Meet",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1980-01_02-paragraph-d3e9bf40b7-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "Saturday, February 9, 10 AM",
      "text_length": 27
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1980-01_02-paragraph-3df803ba20-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "A Beginners and Intermediate meet at Seward Park. Meet at the picnic area on top of the hill at 10 AM. Director of the meet is Charlie Bock. Remember: stick to the paths and roads or you'll end up in the brambles. Good meet for a rainy day as there's not too much traveling on non-paved areas.",
      "text_length": 293
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1980-01_02-heading-ffcea4a3a8-1",
      "kind": "heading",
      "text": "Meeting",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1980-01_02-paragraph-96876908b4-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "Tuesday Monday, February 11, 7 PM",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1980-01_02-paragraph-763b7620f4-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "THE annual business meeting of the Cascade Orienteering Club. Beginners Intro at 7 PM, and meeting at 7:30 PM - annual report of the club, audit of books completed, and short program to follow.",
      "text_length": 193
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1980-01_02-heading-89ddb11840-3",
      "kind": "heading",
      "text": "Meet",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1980-01_02-paragraph-d0c3e57fb2-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "Saturday, February 23, 10 AM",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1980-01_02-paragraph-b23d382207-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "A beginners and Intermediate course at Discovery Park. Meet at the Visitors Center, 10 AM. Director is Mike Schuh.",
      "text_length": 114
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1980-01_02-heading-89ddb11840-4",
      "kind": "heading",
      "text": "Meet",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1980-01_02-paragraph-f8d3519223-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "Saturday, March 8, 10 AM",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1980-01_02-paragraph-01524b030c-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "Again a double course event for the beginner and intermediate. Meet at St. Edwards State Park in Kirkland (pick up Juanita Drive and follow to NE 145th, the park entrance, and follow red/white markers to the registration area). Meet directors are Gary and Debbie MacDonald\u2014who did all the original trail mappings with Charlie Bock in November\u2014now they're on their own.",
      "text_length": 368
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1980-01_02-heading-25399abe92-1",
      "kind": "heading",
      "text": "Possible Meet",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1980-01_02-paragraph-33cbd04ac7-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "Late March",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "block_id": "1980-01_02-paragraph-9b5304cc1e-1",
      "kind": "paragraph",
      "text": "Len Englund is trying to set up a cross-country skiing and orienteering meet with the Konigsberger Ski club at Snoqualmie Pass.",
      "text_length": 127
    }
  ]
}
